---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { personSchema } from '../../lib/jsonld';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Michael Linder, Solutions Architect, owner of Strali Solutions e.U., based in Carinthia, Austria." jsonLd={personSchema}>
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">About</h1>

    <div class="prose mt-10">
      <p>
        I'm Michael Linder, owner of <a href="https://strali.solutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Strali Solutions e.U.</a>, based in Noetsch im Gailtal, Carinthia, Austria. Currently contracting for an international semiconductor manufacturer: software architecture, AI integration, platform templates, and technology strategy. The team builds intranet applications, workflows, and internal platforms. I design the architectures and bring AI into the mix where it makes sense.
      </p>
      <p>
        On the side, I advise SMEs on IT topics through Strali Solutions: Microsoft 365, security, AI strategy, infrastructure. No buzzword consulting, just solutions that work in practice.
      </p>

      <h2>Key Facts</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>20+ years in Enterprise IT: from .NET to SharePoint to AI integration</li>
        <li>Full-service IT consulting for SMEs through Strali Solutions: M365, security, AI, infrastructure</li>
        <li>Contractor: Senior Solutions Architect in the semiconductor industry</li>
        <li>Interest in AI Governance & EU AI Act, writing about it</li>
        <li>Owner of Strali Solutions e.U., Carinthia, Austria</li>
        <li>Radio amateur OE8YML, contributor at oeradio.at</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Beyond IT</h2>
      <p>
        Most importantly: father to Tamara and human to three dogs (Kiki, King and Neo). When I'm not at the screen, I'm out in the mountains, on the radio as OE8YML, or tinkering with new ideas using a soldering iron, wood, 3D printer, or whatever the project needs. I love learning new things. Based in Carinthia.
      </p>

      <h2>This Site</h2>
      <p>
        My personal corner of the internet. I write about things I'm learning, problems I've solved, and occasionally about topics beyond tech.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Best way is <a href="mailto:michael.linder@rednil.at">email</a>. For professional enquiries, reach out via <a href="https://strali.solutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">strali.solutions</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can also find me on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/achildrenmile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>, <a href="https://github.com/achildrenmile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> and <a href="https://x.com/achildrenmile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
